= ∫ 0 1 ( 1 − x ) x 2 n + 1 f ( 2 n + 1 ) ( x ) d x ,</p><p>利用涉及多个函数的H&#246;lder不等式(见 [<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="hanspub.39788-ref1">1</xref>] )，有</p><p>[ ( 2 n + 1 ) ! ] 2 n + 3 = ( ∫ 0 1 ( 1 − x ) x x ⋯ x f ( 2 n + 1 ) ( x ) d x ) 2 n + 3 ≤ ( ∑ k = 1 2 n + 1 ∫ 0 1 x 2 n + 3 d x ) ∫ 0 1 ( 1 − x ) 2 n + 3 d x ∫ 0 1 | f ( 2 n + 1 ) ( x ) | 2 n + 3 d x = [ 1 2 ( n + 2 ) ] 2 ( n + 1 ) ∫ 0 1 | f ( 2 n + 1 ) ( x ) | 2 n + 3 d x ,</p><p>于是得到</p><p>∫ 0 1 | f ( 2 n + 1 ) ( x ) | 2 n + 3 d x ≥ [ 2 ( n + 2 ) ] 2 ( n + 1 ) [ ( 2 n + 1 ) ! ] 2 n + 3 .</p></sec><sec id="s5"><title>文章引用</title><p>吴春阳,洪 勇. 一个涉及Beta函数积分不等式的多种推广Some Extensions of an Integral Inequality with Beta Function[J]. 理论数学, 2021, 11(01): 32-36. https://doi.org/10.12677/PM.2021.111005</p></sec><sec id="s6"><title>参考文献</title></sec></body><back><ref-list><title>References</title><ref id="hanspub.39788-ref1"><label>1</label><mixed-citation publication-type="other" xlink:type="simple">数学手册编写组. 数学手册[M]. 北京: 人民教育出版社, 1997: 20-22.</mixed-citation></ref><ref id="hanspub.39788-ref2"><label>2</label><mixed-citation publication-type="other" xlink:type="simple">陈纪修, 於崇华, 金路. 数学分析(下册) [M]. 北京: 高等教育出版社, 2000: 372-382.</mixed-citation></ref></ref-list></back></article>